Yawan wadanda tsunami ya kashe a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia ya karu zuwa 832, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Kasa da Kasa a safiyar Lahadi.
A wani taron manema labarai, kakakin hukumar Sutopa Purvo Nugroho ya ce, bisa ga rahotanni, mutane da dama sun makale a cikin rugujewar gine-gine da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 da ta auku a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayin mita 7.
Garin na Palo, wanda ke da mutane sama da 380,000, ya cika da baraguron gine-gine.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 bisa zargin kisan kai bayan an yi wa wata mata bulala.
An fara binciken kisan bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside da safiyar yau.
An gano wata mata mai shekaru 44 da haihuwa da karfe 7:55 na safe da raunukan wuka a unguwar Grayson Mues a John Street, kuma an kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 da haihuwa bisa zargin kisan kai.
'Yan sanda sun bukaci mutanen yankin da suka ga ko kuma suka ji wani abu su tuntube su.
Brian O'Hagan, mai binciken ya ce, "Binciken na kan farko ne, amma ina so in nemi duk wanda ya kasance a kusa da John Street a Birkenhead ko ya ga ko ya ji wani abu mai ban mamaki, kuma in nemi su tuntube mu".
