Lokacin da Trump ya yi jawabi a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A wannan yammacin a garin Wheeling, West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da kamfen din hannun jari mai yawa.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake tabbatar da zaben da za a yi domin cike wa babban kotun kasar, Trump na neman kara goyon bayan zaben da za a yi a lokacin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa idan aka kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne jawabin Trump zai fara a yammacin yau a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon sa a intanet?
Trump zai yi jawabi a garin Wheeling, West Virginia, da misalin karfe 7 na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa a matsayin live a YouTube.
Trump na iya yin la'akari da sauraron karar da aka yi a wannan makon kan takarar Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli, wanda ke fuskantar kalubalen zargin cin zarafin mata, tare da amincewa da ake sa ran za a yi a majalisar dattawa a cikin mako guda a yayin binciken FBI.
Amma babban dalilin wannan jawabi shi ne don taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Kamfanin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya sanar da cewa jawabai biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin karawa masu sa kai da magoya baya karfi yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai a ajandar sa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya, yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da tashin hankali", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump.
An shirya taron na yau a filin wasan Wesbanco Arena da ke Willing, wanda zai iya jawo hankalin magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia Patrick Morris, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morris cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi ci gaba a zaben", in ji Simon Heder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
