Turai ta kai wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder da ci 10-6
Turai za ta samu nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan ta samu nasara daga wasannin ranar Asabar da maki hudu da hudu da nasara 10-6 akan Amurka.
Wani dan wasa mai suna Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Malinari ne suka jagoranci gasar tare da cin nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods don kawo sakamakon Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
Yankin Turai na Thomas Bjorn, yana kokarin ceton kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye rashin jin daɗin Amurka da safe, ya ci wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da babbar juriya a wasan kwallon hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya yin fiye da haka ba.
Don adana kofin, ƙungiyar Jim Furyk tana buƙatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa a ranar Lahadi.
