Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed da kwallaye hudu, sun yi nasara sosai wajen doke Woods da dan wasan Amurka na farko, Bryson DeComb, da ci 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya gudanar da kansa a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wani ɗan lokaci na haske, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin 29 sau a wasanni hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
