Kallon nasarar da Jacob Cagan ya yi ya sa Craig Hulket ya yi jinkiri, amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya iya buga wani babban rauni daga baya.
Rangers sun mallaki wasan, amma a cikin kashi na uku na karshe, sun fi fatan cin kwallo fiye da nuna wasa mai kyau.
Alfred Marelas tabbas ya kamata a yi masa tara da kwata-kwata sa'a daya kafin a gama lokacin da shi da Stephen Lawless suka yi karo a filin, amma Alkali Stephen Thomson bai amince da korafin Columbia ba.
Rangers sun yi nasarar buga ƙofar ne kawai a farkon rabin wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Aybrocks Liam Kelly ya kusan ba da burin Lassan Kulibaly da kuma mummunan harin Ovyi Eheria.
Duk da cewa bayan da suka zura kwallo ta farko a minti na 34, Livi ya yi watsi da ci gaba da wasa, amma babu wanda ya musanta cewa dole ne su nuna wa magoya baya wasa mai kyau.
Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya shiga cikin ƙofar Jacobs ba.
Scott Orfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da izinin Scott Robinson, wanda ya toshe Mingo don samun damar buga ƙofar.
Gerard ya maye gurbin Culibaly da Ryan Kent a lokacin hutu, kuma hakan ya yi tasiri sosai lokacin da dan wasan ya kai Marelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya gudu ya toshe harbi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da nishadantar da masu sauraronsa ta hanyar buga wasan da suka fi so, kuma Lithgow da Hulket sun ci gaba da raba kwallon bayan dogon lokaci.
Bock Holt ya iya rinjaye kawai a minti na karshe, amma McGregor ya buga da kyau don tsayayya da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya tafi benci.
Sauya Rangers zuwa Glenn Middleton ya sake faruwa bayan hukuncin kisa, lokacin da ya fuskanci Jacobs, amma Thompson ya yi nasara ya kauce masa.
