Wannan hanya ta hada da daukar kwayoyin garkuwar jikin mutum daga cikin marasa lafiya, canza su a dakin gwaje-gwaje domin su iya gano furotin HER2, wanda ya zama ruwan dare ga kwayoyin ciwon daji da yawa, sannan a sake shigar da su.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky ne ya bayyana hakan daga cibiyar kula da ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa akwai rigakafin da ke da matukar alfanu.
HER2 yana kara bunkasa wasu nau'o'in kwayoyin cutar sankara da ke yaki da cutar sankarar nono, ta ovarian, da kuma na huhu, "in ji Farfesa Berezofsky.
