HIV/AIDS: China ta ruwaito karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14%
China ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
A cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya, sama da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka ana yada su ne ta hanyar jima'i, kamar yadda aka yi a baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa a wasu yankunan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
"Amma yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar HIV ta hanyar jinin da aka basu ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili", jami'an kasar Sin sun fada a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin na karuwa da mutum 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i  babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT a China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna wa LGBT wariya.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar, kimanin kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza, a karshe suna auren mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna yaduwa ne saboda rashin ilimi da kuma maganin hana haihuwa.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar ta duniya.
