Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin barazana ta hanyar amfani da tallace-tallace na yaɗa labarai
Mako guda bayan jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi hudu na talla a wata jaridar Amurka mai ɗaukaka fa'idodin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ambaci shafin China Daily a ranar Laraba a cikin Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa  bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattawa na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba. Wannan zargi ne da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa China na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka kira a cikin wata hira da Reuters sabon mataki a yakin neman matsin lamba na Washington akan China.
Ko da yake tallace-tallace da gwamnatocin kasashen waje ke yi na inganta kasuwanci, yanzu Beijing da Washington sun kaddamar da yakin kasuwanci wanda ya haifar da sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
Masana Amurka da China sun ce an saka takunkumin ne don cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki kamar 'yan kasuwa na Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstead, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
China, in ji Branstad a cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, yanzu tana kara kokarinta ta hanyar buga talla a jaridarmu mai 'yanci.
"A yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da kyawawan al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da kuma 'yancin latsawa ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstead.
"Idan ka duba kantunan jaridu a Beijing, ba za ka ga masu adawa da yawa ba, kuma ba za ka ga wani tunani na ra'ayin da Sin ke da shi game da yanayin tattalin arziki mai hadari ba, saboda gaskiyar cewa jarida tana karkashin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin".
Ya kara da cewa, "daya daga cikin jaridun kasar Sin mafi tasiri ya ki amincewa da buga labarinsa, ko da yake bai ambaci sunan jaridar ba".
'Yan Republican sun kori mata daga zaben da za su yi kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara, masu sharhi sun ce Kavanaugh ya gaza
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke kare dan takarar babban alkalin kotun Burt Kavanaugh a gaban zargin cin zarafin mata da dama, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su fuskanci hari, musamman daga mata, a zaben da ke tafe.
An samu tashin hankali sosai game da wannan, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna shirye su yi zabe.
