"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Corinne Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta ihu "November soon!" a yayin zanga-zangar da aka yi a zauren majalisar dattawa, lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar gabatar da Kavanaugh, duk da sanarwar Dr. Christina Blasey Ford, a cewar Mic.
"Himma da kuma kwarin gwiwar 'yan Democrat zai kasance mai girma", in ji Stu Rottenberg, wani mai sharhi kan harkokin siyasa mai zaman kansa, ga shafin yanar gizo na labarai.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun yi tsayi, kuma gaskiya ne.
