Firist na Anglican kawai da aka ba shi Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin mai shiga cikin yaƙe-yaƙe, an yi bikin a garinsu bayan shekaru 100.
An ba da kyautar mai suna Bernard Van a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba na 1918 don shiga cikin harin da aka kai a Belengliz da Leakur.
Amma bayan kwana hudu, wani dan bindiga ya harbe shi, bai san cewa ya sami babbar lambar yabo ta soja ba.
