Saukowa da wani sabon Jamus warship sake jinkirta
Sabon jirgin ruwan na sojin ruwan Jamus ya kamata ya fara aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai bayyana ba sai shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ba shi da inganci da kuma hauhawar farashi, a cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na cikin gida.
Saukowar Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin sabon nau'in jirgi na Baden-Wuerttemberg, an jinkirta shi zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta rubuta, tana mai ambaton wani jami'in soji.
An shirya jirgin ya fara aiki a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka taso bayan gina shi sun hana wannan aikin.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, wadanda aka yi oda tun a 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan na Bremen.
Za su kasance dauke da manyan bindigogi, da wasu makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohin stel, kamar su rage ganuwa ga radars, infrared da kuma sautin sa hannu.
Daga cikin wasu muhimman halaye  tsawon lokaci tsakanin sabis  sabbin jiragen ruwa na iya kasa shiga tashar jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Koyaya, jinkiri na yau da kullun yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na zamani  waɗanda zasu iya ba Jamus damar nuna ƙarfinta a wajen ƙasar  sun tsufa kafin a ƙarshe su shiga cikin aiki, Die Zeit ta lura.
Frigate F125 da aka yi rashin nasara ya shiga cikin kanun labarai a bara lokacin da Rundunar Sojan Ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin a hukumance kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
A karo na farko Sojojin Ruwa sun mayar da jirgin zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun rubuta game da yawancin "raunin software da kayan aiki" wanda ke sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a cikin aikin yaƙi.
Rashin inganci na software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg suna da masu aikin jirgin ruwa 120 kawai  rabin ma'aikatan tsoffin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
Har ila yau, jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ya rage yawan aikinsa kuma ya iyakance yiwuwar sabuntawa.
Rhinland-Pfalz yana da nauyin tan 7000, wanda ya ninka nauyin jiragen ruwa na irin wannan aji da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga kayan aikin da suka lalace, farashin duk aikin  ciki har da horar da ma'aikata  kuma ya zama matsala.
Farashin ya kai Euro biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6)  duk da cewa da farko ya kai Euro biliyan 2.2
Matsalolin da ke tattare da sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken gargaɗin kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro a majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya bayyana cewa rundunar sojin ruwan "tana da jiragen ruwa masu ƙarancin ƙarfi da za su iya yin aikin soja".
Ya ce matsalar tana karuwa ne a tsawon lokaci, saboda tsoffin jiragen ruwa suna rushewa, kuma babu wasu jiragen ruwa da za a maye gurbin su.
Ya koka cewa babu ɗayan jirage masu saukar ungulu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Rundunar Sojan Ruwa.
