A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, a cewar jami'ai.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
A cikin Palau, sama da mutane 16,000 aka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Pulau da Dongola a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiya Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala  regency, wanda ya shimfiɗa a kan fiye da mil 180 (300 km) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regency  yanki ne na yanki wanda ke ƙasa da lardin, a cikin 2017 ya ƙunshi mutane 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci ga lardin, amma galibi an mai da hankali ne a Moravali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia, an yi wa Palau da Donggala barazanar tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami a Donggala ya kashe mutane sama da 200, kuma ɗaruruwan gidaje sun lalace.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin yankin na Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ke da tasirin girgizar kasa a cikin tekun Pacific kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar kasa.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: jerin girgizar kasa masu karfin gaske sun afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris zuwa farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gabar kudu, inda ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Garin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra, ya yi girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentovai a wajen Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa yankin Pidi Jaya na lardin Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da ta tunatar da mutane da raunin da girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarar 2004 suka yi.
Ba a samu tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 suka mutu a cikin rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Lambock na Indonesia, inda ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido ba su da damar fita.
An kama babban dan Sara Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Treck Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, bisa zargin kai harin.
An kama Palin mai shekara 29 daga Basilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, wanda ya sabawa rahotanni game da cin zarafin cikin gida da kuma adawa da kama da aka wallafa ranar Asabar da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, lokacin da wata mata da ta san ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton wani laifi, sai 'yan sanda suka kwace wayar ta.
A cewar tashar KTUU, Palin yana cikin gidan yarin na Matanuska-Susitna a karkashin jinginar dala 500.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana cewa shi "ba shi da laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko ya yarda da laifinsa, in ji hanyar sadarwa.
An zargi Palin da laifuffuka guda uku na aji A, wanda zai iya kaiwa ga shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da aikata laifi na aji B, wanda ake azabtar da shi da ɗaurin kurkuku na kwana ɗaya da tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka zargi Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017 aka zarge shi da kai hari kan mahaifinsa Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su sanar da su cewa an kai hari.
Yanzu haka shari'ar tana gaban kotun tsaron Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an gurfanar da shi kan zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, karya rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida da kuma rike da makami a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta yi ikirarin cewa ya buge ta a fuska.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 saboda alakar halin ɗanta na zalunci da ciwon ciwon kai bayan ciwon da ya haifar da aikinsa a Iraki.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia sun kashe daruruwan mutane
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka rasa rayukansu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afku ne kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin Indonesia.
An yada bidiyo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin da aka yi harin.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palo, lokacin da tsunami ya afka bakin teku.
Ofishin Jakadancin Tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na wani wanda ake zargi da kai harin New York
Ofishin kotun tarayya na birnin New York na neman a yanke wa Saiful Saifov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953 saboda laifukan tarayya.
Saipow, mai shekara 30, a watan Oktoba an ce ya yi amfani da motar motar kamfanin Home Depot don hawa kan hanyar keke a gefen yammacin Manhattan, yana doke masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a hanyarsa.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, bisa ga sanarwar da aka gabatar na neman hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin New York, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipow "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni.
Dangane da bayanan kotu, za a iya hukunta laifuffukan biyu da hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kwamishinan bincike na tarayya ya mamaye Saipov da gabatar da tuhuma mai abubuwa 22, wanda ya hada da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai don tallafawa fashin kwamfuta, wanda aka saba amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in masu gabatar da kara na tarayya game da aikata laifuka masu tsari, da kuma aikata tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
A cewar masu gabatar da kara, harin ya bukaci shiryawa da gangan, kuma yayin bayyana laifin da Saif ya aikata, sun yi amfani da kalmomin kamar m, mai tsanani da kuma lalata.
Saifullah Habilouayevich Saipow ya yi rauni, ya lalata kuma ya jawo asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anna-Lori Decadett, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlia, Ernan Feruch, Ernan Diego Mendas da Alejandro Damiano Pagnock, an bayyana a cikin sanarwar niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka fara shari'ar kisa a yankin kudancin birnin New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma Hallid Barnes hukuncin kisa na masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu, amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekarar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa a birnin New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin shekaru biyu da suka gabata saboda laifin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Cacar Baki.
An kashe ma'aurata Rosenberg a kan kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipow, wanda asalinsa Uzbekistan ne, bisa ga takardun kotu, ya nuna rashin laifi a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
A cewar 'yan sanda, ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin dadin abin da ya yi.
A cewar karar da ake tuhumar, Saipow ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa kallon bidiyon Islama a wayar sa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
Ya kuma nemi izinin rataye tutar kungiyar IS a dakin asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya amsa laifinsa a cikin hukuncin da aka yanke masa na abubuwa 22.
David Paton, daya daga cikin masu kare hakkin jama'a na tarayya, wanda ke wakiltar Saifov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da shawarar da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Muna ganin hukuncin kisa maimakon daurin rai da rai ba tare da damar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita azabar da wadannan abubuwan suka jawo wa duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Pathan.
Kungiyar kare Saipow ta taba rokon masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
