Gasar Elite: Dandy Stars  Belfast Giants 5-3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a wasan da Dundee ya yi da Giants
Dundee Stars sun yi nasara a ranar Juma'a da suka sha kashi a hannun Belfast Giants a gasar Elite League, inda suka ci wasan da suka yi a gida 5-3 a ranar Asabar.
Sakamakon bugun Patrick Dwyer da Francis Bavilier, Giants sun jagoranci da kwallaye biyu a farkon.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cooney sun daidaita kafin Dwyer ya sake kafa Giants a kan gaba.
François Boucher daga Dundee ya daidaita lissafin, bayan haka Lucas Lundwald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar Adam Keefe ta sha kaye a gasar Elite a kakar bana, bayan da ta doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da yamma.
Kungiyoyin sun hadu a karo na hudu a kakar wasa; a cikin wasanni uku da suka gabata sun ci Giants.
Wasan farko a minti na huɗu na wasan (03:35) ya zira Dwyer daga ƙaddamar da Kendall McFollow, kuma bayan minti huɗu Bavilier ya ninka lambar bayan ƙaddamar da David Rutherford.
A cikin lokacin farko mai cike da tashin hankali (13:10), Sullivan ya buɗe ƙidayar daga hannun masu filin, sannan kuma Kaun ya daidaita ƙidayar bayan da Matt Markward ya ba da izinin (15:16).
Dwyer ya tabbatar da Giants a matsayin jagora a lokacin da ya fara hutu na farko, ya zira kwallo na biyu a wasan a ƙarshen farkon lokacin.
