Dalilin da yasa yakin cinikayya tsakanin China da Amurka zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Farkon tashin hankali na yakin cinikayya tsakanin Sin da Amurka ya kasance mai ban tsoro, kuma tunda yakin bai kare ba, a cikin dogon lokaci rashin fahimta tsakanin kasashen na iya zama da fa'ida ga Beijing, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar, inda ya sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru ne a wannan makon, lokacin da sabbin harajin suka shafi kayayyaki masu daraja dala biliyan 200 (£ biliyan 150), a zahiri suna biyan haraji kan rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka yi wannan, Beijing ta mayar da martani ta hanyar kara haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa kashi 10 a kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi wa Amurka alkawarin amsawa, kuma tattalin arzikin ta biyu mafi girma a duniya ba zai taba gani ba.
Don a sa Washington ta ja da baya, ana bukatar a yi karin kira, amma nuna goyon baya ga Amurka a fili ba shi da kyau ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da yanayin yadda ya kamata, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya na Amurka na iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci, yana rage dogaro da kasashen biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani matakin siyasa na gaggawa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai fara wani tsari na raguwar tattalin arziki ya fi yadda masu sa ido suka yi tsammani, "in ji Abigail Grace, mataimakin mai bincike da ke da ƙwarewa a Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabon Tsaron Amurka.
Syria a shirye take ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Syria ta bayyana cewa tana shirye don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar kuma ta yi kira ga taimakon sake gina kasar da aka lalata ta da yakin da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Mu'alem ya ce, yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, halin da ake ciki a kasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro, saboda ci gaban da ake samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da rayuwa ta al'ada.
Yanzu muna da dukkan yanayi domin 'yan gudun hijira su koma kasashen da suka tilasta su bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma niyya tattalin arziki da matakan da aka yi niyya don inganta rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma hanyar da rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar na bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Mu'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi farin cikin karbar taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Sai dai ya jaddada cewa kasar ba za ta amince da taimakon da aka yi mata ba a kan wasu sharudda ko kuma tallafi daga kasashen da ke tallafawa 'yan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe Kofin Ryder na 2018, ta doke tawagar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin Le Golf National a kewayen Paris, Faransa.
Amurka za ta yi rashin nasara a karo na shida a jere a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin lokacin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5, wadanda ake bukata don cin Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi kokawa a gasar, ya kori kwallonsa a cikin ruwa a 3 na 16th hole, ya ba da wannan wasan ga Francesco Malinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Malinarri ya yi fice a duk zagaye, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka wuce wannan filin tare da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a cikin tsarin yanzu a 1979.
Jordan Spice na Amurka ya yi nasara da maki 5 da 4 daga dan wasan da ya fi kasa da matsayi a kungiyar Turai, Thornbjörn Olsen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda wataƙila ya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
Tsohon soja na gasar cin kofin Ryder takwas dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan da ya fi kowa lashe gasar tare da ci 25,5 a cikin aikinsa.
