Bayanan Red Tide: Ragewar ruwa a Pinellas, Manati da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga kwamitin kiyaye kifaye da namun daji na Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan ruwan sama a wasu sassan Tampa Bay.
A cewar bayanin kwamitin, an bayar da rahoton wasu wuraren da suke fure a cikin Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Charlotte da Callie, wanda ke nufin raguwar taro.
Furewar Red Tide tana gudana kimanin mil 130 (200 km) na gabar teku daga arewacin gundumar Pinellas zuwa kudancin gundumar Lee.
Ana iya samun wasu furannin a wajen mil 10 daga gabar teku a gundumar Hillsborough, amma yawan su na raguwa daga makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga jan ruwa a gundumar Easter.
Matsakaicin girman ma'adinai a bakin teku ko kusa da bakin teku a gundumar Pinellas ya bayyana a makon da ya gabata, a Hillsborough ma'adinai sun kasance daga low zuwa high. a cikin Manatee game da baya zuwa high, a bakin teku ko kusa da bakin teku a gundumar Saratoga ma'adinai sun kasance daga baya zuwa high, a cikin gundumar Charlotte daga baya zuwa matsakaici, a bakin teku ko kusa da bakin teku a gundumar Lee game da baya zuwa high kuma a cikin gundumar Callie ƙananan ma'adinai.
An samu rahoton tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin numfashi a cikin Pinellas County, Manati, Sarasota, Lee da Callie.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani rahoton cutar numfashi da aka samu daga arewa maso yammacin Florida.
